"{\"uid\": \"enstarz.com-articles-235205-20240730-blue-man-at-paris-olympic-opening-ceremony-defends-his-performance-despite-growing-up-christian-wants-forgiveness.htm\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony of the Paris 2024 Olympics caused massivecontroversyfrom viewers who say the performance mocked Christianity's 'The Last Supper.'\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9466740785882145, \"rank\": 0.05632862513374173, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, participants who performed in the ceremony last week are speaking out.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to 'CNN,' Philippe Katerine, a French entertainer, was dubbed \\\"the blue man,\\\" who portrayed the Greek god of wine Dionysus.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 243, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.4801888396721913e-11, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}, {\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippe Katerine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\"}, {\"begin\": 270, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9997251858551085, \"rank\": 0.00026581520473991104, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 335, \"end\": 340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9933546761098778, \"rank\": 0.003098252841649403, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.570030524617596e-16, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While lying on a table seemingly without clothes, Katerine sang a song covered in glittery blue paint from head to toe.\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Katerine told the outlet how his song \\\"Nue\\\" - or \\\"Naked\\\" in English - was a message for peace.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Would there have been wars if we'd stayed naked?\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The answer is perhaps not because you can not hide a gun or a dagger when you are naked,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So you have got this idea of harmlessness when it comes to the naked man.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the idea of the origins of the Olympic Games in Greece - which are represented today because when you see paintings, they are of naked athletes too - also with the idea that they can not carry weapons when they are naked.\\\"\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9928428393351576, \"rank\": 0.007182899393849782, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The interpretation of the Greek God Dionysus makes us aware of the absurdity of violence between human beings.#Paris2024#OpeningCeremonypic.twitter.com/FBlQNNUmvV    He continued: \\\"So there I came, simply, to sing this song.\\\"\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9933546761098778, \"rank\": 0.003098252841649403, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.570030524617596e-16, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED :2024 Paris Olympics Organizers Apologize For 'Offensive' Opening Ceremony, Largest Sponsor Pulls Advertising For 'Unacceptable Mockery'  Katerine, a songwriter, said he was \\\"deeply sorry\\\" if his appearance offended any of the millions of viewers and that his intention was a \\\"misunderstanding.\\\"\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was brought up as a Christian and the best thing about Christianity is forgiveness,\\\" he told 'CNN.'\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9441134455996087, \"rank\": 0.05916593736664206, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9466740785882145, \"rank\": 0.05632862513374173, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.4801888396721913e-11, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, it's the most beautiful thing there is: forgiveness.\\\"\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw something very colorful, reconciliatory and peaceful,\\\" Katerine stated, adding he was \\\"surprised\\\" by the backlash, despite his frustration the International Olympic Committee (IOC) refused to use subtitles.\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1881, \"end\": 1918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1881, \"end\": 1918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I ask for forgiveness if I have offended anyone, and the Christians of the world will grant me that, I am sure, and will understand that it was mostly a misunderstanding,\\\" the performer said.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because when it comes down to it, it wasn't about representing 'The Last Supper' at all.\\\"\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aside from enraged viewers, one of the largest sponsors of the Paris Olympics quickly pulled their advertising due to what they deem an \\\"unacceptable mockery.\\\"\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED :Olympics 2024 'Last Supper' Drag Performer Threatens To Sue Critics As More Celebs Defend Opening Ceremony  C-Spire - the largest privately-held wireless provider in the USA - declared that they are pulling out altogether.\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2574, \"end\": 2577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999905169617602, \"rank\": 9.480986657513931e-06, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were shocked by the mockery of the Last Supper during the opening ceremonies of the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"C Spire will be pulling our advertising from the Olympics,\\\"the company pennedon Twitter, now X, early Saturday.\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2732, \"end\": 2739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C_Spire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"C Spire\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C_Spire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C_Spire\"}, {\"begin\": 2812, \"end\": 2819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 0.999999999986585, \"rank\": 1.3384013833966227e-11, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The post hit over 9 million views and received a flood of positive responses.\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 Enstarz.com All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not reproduce without permission.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2999, \"entities\": []}]}"